description:
Call ERASMUS-EDU-2024-PEX-EMJM-MOB has closed on 15 February 2024.
140 proposals have been submitted.
Evaluation results are expected to be communicated in July 2024.&nbsp;
&nbsp;

Call ERASMUS-EDU-2024-EMJM-DESIGN has closed on 15 February 2024.
178 proposals have been submitted.
Evaluation results are expected to be communicated in July 2024.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
&nbsp;

&nbsp;
The list of non-EU Participating Countries in the Creative Europe Programme was updated on 01.02.2024 due to the level of participation limited to the Culture strand and the Creative Europe Desks action for Montenegro and Tunisia.
&nbsp;

The submission session is now available for:  ERC-2018-PoC (ERC-POC).

Please note that the submission to ERC-2018-POC call is done using the html 5 technology.
See our useful tips in this ERC-2018-PoC HTML5 instructions guide.

Please get familiar with the submission system ahead the deadline to avoid encountering unforeseen problems at submission.
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
&nbsp;

&nbsp;
Helpdesk closure
The last day to send questions to the IF 2023 Auction Call Helpdesk is 25/01/2024. Questions received after this date will not be replied.&nbsp;
The deadline for submission of proposals is on 08/02/2024 at 17h00 Brussels time.
